article.description: — Travis Evee had 18 points as Rice topped New Orleans 73-62 on Monday.
article.headline: Evee lifts Rice past New Orleans 73-62
article.linkText: Evee lifts Rice past New Orleans 73-62
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Travis Evee had 18 points as Rice topped New Orleans 73-62 on Monday. Riley Abercrombie and Quincy Olivari each added 14 points for Rice (6-2). Rodney Carson Jr. had 15 points for the Privateers (1-7), whose losing streak reached four games. Lamont Berzat added 14 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
